item.title: Compiler doesnt run why?!?!
item.dc:creator: @MrMoney MrMoney
item.description:
@MrMoney wrote:

@echo off
title Easy Compiler V1
echo Please Wait…
if exist “%programfiles%\Java” (call :compile “%programfiles%\Java”)
:compile
for /D %%x in ("%~1jdk*") do (set p="%%~x\bin\javac.exe")
if defined p (%p% -cp . *.java)
if defined p (goto end)
:end
pause
exit
